snippet.title: Introduction to Last Remains
snippet.description:
Think you know everything about Last Remains? Watch this intro video as we give the lowdown on the basics, the gameplay, and a few survival tips. 

Welcome to Last Remains - the first AAA web3 zombie battle royale!

Website: https://www.lastremains.gg/
Litepaper: https://litepaper.lastremains.gg/
